==Bosnian==
===Proper noun===
'''Srbijanac''' ''m s''
#a [[Serb]], a citizen of [[Serbia]] (not necessarily of [[Serb]] ethnicity). The term is considered to be slightly derogatory; the adjectiv [[Serbian]] should be used instead (Eg.  She is Serbian). 
